                                                    <p>You will comply with all applicable export laws and restrictions and regulations of the Indian Department of Commerce and Industry, or other Indian or foreign agency or authority, and you will not use the Services to export, or allow any export or re-export in violation of any such restrictions, laws or regulations. You represent and warrant to Fitness Pro League that you are not a prohibited party or located in, under the control of, or a national or resident of any restricted country, and that you will otherwise comply with all applicable export control laws. If you reside outside the India, then in addition to complying with the foregoing, you will comply with any relevant export control laws in your local jurisdiction.</p>
